Undefeated;;89;;96;;PG-13;;Since its founding in 1899, Manassas High School in North Memphis has never had a football team win a playoff game. In 2004, former high-school coach Bill Courtney offers to help turn the Manassas Tigers around. Nurturing his players' physical and emotional strengths, Courtney's efforts pay off in 2009, when the Tigers, led by their star player O.C., seem to have a chance to break their school's 110-year losing streak and finally win a playoff game.;;Documentary;;Dan Lindsay,T.J. Martin;;2012;;Bill Courtney;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/undefeated_2012